# Tool Orchestrator Tests

This directory contains tests for the tool orchestrator package.

## Test Categories

- **Unit Tests**: Individual tool adapter and runner tests
- **Integration Tests**: End-to-end tool execution flow tests
- **Permission Tests**: Bot tool access control validation
- **Health Tests**: Tool health monitoring tests
- **Fallback Tests**: Tool fallback and recovery tests

## Running Tests

```
bash
npm test
npm run test:watch
npm run test:coverage
```

## Test Organization

- `tool-runner.test.ts` - Tool execution tests
- `tool-registry.test.ts` - Registry lookup tests
- `tool-permissions.test.ts` - Permission validation tests
- `tool-health.test.ts` - Health monitoring tests
- `tool-fallback.test.ts` - Fallback chain tests
- `e2e/tool-execution.test.ts` - End-to-end tests
